  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delivery Service : Courier is a competitive game where you become a delivery man and the person who earns more money wins.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Players must select the delivery they want, pick up boxes from the delivery's starting point, and deliver them to the destination.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You can earn delivery commissions by completing deliveries.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you run out of fuel before reaching the gas station, you'll have to walk to the gas station to buy more fuel and refuel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be sure to arrive at the gas station and refuel before your truck runs out of fuel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delivery allowances can be invested in stocks, real estate, etc.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please be aware that violating traffic laws may result in fines.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Play Time</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30-60 minutes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Key Description</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WASD : Moving</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>E : Get in or out of the truck</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>C : Fuel charging</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Q : Mini-Map</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> I  : Cell Phone</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delivery Service : Courier is a competitive game where you become a delivery man and the person who earns more money wins.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Players must select the delivery they want, pick up boxes from the delivery's starting point, and deliver them to the destination.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You can earn delivery commissions by completing deliveries.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If you run out of fuel before reaching the gas station, you'll have to walk to the gas station to buy more fuel and refuel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be sure to arrive at the gas station and refuel before your truck runs out of fuel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delivery allowances can be invested in stocks, real estate, etc.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please be aware that violating traffic laws may result in fines.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Play Time</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30-60 minutes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Key Description</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WASD : Moving</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>E : Get in or out of the truck</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>C : Fuel charging</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Q : Mini-Map</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> I  : Cell Phone</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
